<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Become a GetPro Partner | GetPro</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Become a GetPro Partner — list your professional services, reach clients across Zambia, and grow your business with a clear profile and partner support."
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css?v=20260322a" />
  </head>
  <body class="join-page">
    <a href="/" class="join-top-brand" id="join-top-brand" aria-label="GetPro home">
      <div class="logo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <span class="join-top-brand-title">GetPro</span>
    </a>

    <section class="join-hero" id="join-hero">
      <div class="container join-hero-inner">
        <h1>Become a GetPro Partner</h1>
        <p class="join-lead">
          Tell us what you do and where you operate. GetPro helps people in Zambia find trusted professionals — join the directory and we’ll walk you through the next steps.
        </p>

        <div class="join-tiles" aria-label="Why partner with GetPro">
          <div class="join-tiles-grid">
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                  <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
                  <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
                  <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">Reach the right clients</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">Show up when people search your profession and city — your profile is built for discovery.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2" />
                  <path d="M3 9h18" />
                  <path d="M9 21V9" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">One clear profile</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">Keep services, contact options, and your story in one professional page — easy for customers to trust.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10" />
                  <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">Quality-first directory</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">We review partner applications so the marketplace stays credible for homeowners and businesses.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">Leads that fit you</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">Visitors can reach you directly from your profile — fewer missed opportunities, clearer conversations.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                  <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">Fast to start</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">Short registration, then our team follows up with onboarding — no endless forms on day one.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="join-tile">
              <div class="join-tile-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z" />
                  <path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z" />
                  <path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0" />
                  <path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="join-tile-title">Partner support</h3>
              <p class="join-tile-text">We’re here to help you present your business well and make the most of your listing on GetPro.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary join-get-started" id="join-get-started">Get Started</button>

        <div class="join-wizard-frame" id="join-wizard-frame" hidden>
          <section class="join-wizard join-wizard--hidden" id="join-wizard" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="join-wizard-inner">
              <div class="join-progress" role="status" aria-live="polite">
                Step <span id="join-step-num">1</span> of 3
              </div>
              <div class="join-progress-track" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="join-progress-fill" id="join-progress-fill" style="width: 33.33%"></div>
              </div>

              <div id="join-panels">
                <div class="join-step-panel" id="join-step-1" data-step="1">
                  <h2>What is your profession?</h2>
                  <p class="join-step-hint">Choose a service from the list (same as on the home page search).</p>
                  <div class="join-field join-field--ac">
                    <label for="join-profession">Profession</label>
                    <div
                      class="pro-ac join-pro-ac"
                      data-ac-list="service"
                      data-watermark-text="Profession: Electrician"
                    >
                      <input
                        id="join-profession"
                        class="pro-ac-input"
                        type="text"
                        autocomplete="off"
                        role="combobox"
                        aria-autocomplete="list"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="join-profession-dropdown"
                        required
                      />
                      <input type="hidden" class="pro-ac-hidden" id="join-profession-hid" value="" />
                      <ul class="pro-ac-dropdown" id="join-profession-dropdown" role="listbox" hidden></ul>
                      <p class="pro-ac-msg" hidden></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="join-wizard-actions join-wizard-actions--split">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary-wf" id="join-cancel-1">Cancel</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="join-next-1">Continue</button>
                  </div>
                  <p class="join-wizard-error" id="join-error-1" hidden></p>
                </div>

                <div class="join-step-panel" id="join-step-2" data-step="2" hidden>
                  <h2>Which city or town do you work in?</h2>
                  <p class="join-step-hint">Choose where you mainly serve customers (same style as the home page city field).</p>
                  <div class="join-field join-field--ac">
                    <label for="join-city">City</label>
                    <div
                      class="pro-ac join-pro-ac"
                      data-ac-list="city"
                      data-watermark-text="City: Lusaka"
                    >
                      <input
                        id="join-city"
                        class="pro-ac-input"
                        type="text"
                        autocomplete="off"
                        role="combobox"
                        aria-autocomplete="list"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="join-city-dropdown"
                        required
                      />
                      <input type="hidden" class="pro-ac-hidden" id="join-city-hid" value="" />
                      <ul class="pro-ac-dropdown" id="join-city-dropdown" role="listbox" hidden></ul>
                      <p class="pro-ac-msg" hidden></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="join-wizard-actions join-wizard-actions--split">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="join-next-2">Continue</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary-wf" id="join-back-2">Back</button>
                  </div>
                  <p class="join-wizard-error" id="join-error-2" hidden></p>
                </div>

                <div class="join-step-panel" id="join-step-3" data-step="3" hidden>
                  <div id="join-step-3-form">
                    <h2>Your contact details</h2>
                    <p class="join-step-hint">We’ll use this to reach you about your listing</p>
                    <div class="join-field">
                      <label for="join-name">Full name</label>
                      <input
                        id="join-name"
                        name="name"
                        class="join-plain-input"
                        type="text"
                        autocomplete="name"
                        placeholder="e.g. Jane Banda"
                        required
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="join-field">
                      <label for="join-phone">Phone number</label>
                      <input
                        id="join-phone"
                        name="phone"
                        class="join-plain-input"
                        type="tel"
                        autocomplete="tel"
                        placeholder="Digits only, at least 8"
                        required
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="join-wizard-actions join-wizard-actions--split">
                      <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary-wf" id="join-cancel-3">Cancel</button>
                      <div class="join-wizard-actions-right">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary-wf" id="join-back-3">Back</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="join-submit">Submit</button>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="join-wizard-error" id="join-error-3" hidden></p>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    id="join-step-3-thanks"
                    class="join-step-thanks"
                    role="status"
                    aria-live="polite"
                    hidden
                  >
                    <p class="join-step-thanks-message">
                      Thank you, our team shall contact you soon.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div
      class="join-modal-backdrop"
      id="join-exit-modal"
      hidden
      role="dialog"
      aria-modal="true"
      aria-labelledby="join-exit-modal-title"
    >
      <div class="join-modal">
        <h2 class="join-modal-title" id="join-exit-modal-title">Want us to call you?</h2>
        <p class="join-modal-text">Leave registration and we can still reach out if you’d like a call.</p>
        <div class="join-modal-actions">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary-wf" id="join-exit-modal-dismiss">Cancel</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="join-exit-modal-call">Call Me</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/autocomplete.js?v=20260322a"></script>
    <script src="/join.js?v=20260322a"></script>
  </body>
</html>
